    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "optim_text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 488,
      "width": 527,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "AdamW Optimizer — 双参数组\n\nbackbone_params = [img_branch, pc_branch]  → lr × backbone_lr_scale (0.1)\nhead_params = [fuser, transformer, heads]   → lr (full)\nweight_decay = 1e-4\n\n设计: Backbone 使用 1/10 学习率保护预训练权重, 仅微调不破坏\n优化点: 可尝试渐进解冻 (progressive unfreezing) 策略",
      "originalText": "AdamW Optimizer — 双参数组\n\nbackbone_params = [img_branch, pc_branch]  → lr × backbone_lr_scale (0.1)\nhead_params = [fuser, transformer, heads]   → lr (full)\nweight_decay = 1e-4\n\n设计: Backbone 使用 1/10 学习率保护预训练权重, 仅微调不破坏\n优化点: 可尝试渐进解冻 (progressive unfreezing) 策略",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 470005,
