    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sched_text",
      "x": 570,
      "y": 488,
      "width": 530,
      "height": 133,
      "text": "LR Scheduler — Cosine Warm Restarts (推荐)\n\nSequentialLR([\n  LinearLR(start_factor=0.01, total_iters=warmup_epochs=5),\n  CosineAnnealingWarmRestarts(T_0=50, T_mult=2)\n], milestones=[warmup_epochs])\n\n周期: 50 → 100 → 200 epochs (T_mult=2 翻倍)\n备选: StepLR(step_size=80, gamma=0.5)",
      "originalText": "LR Scheduler — Cosine Warm Restarts (推荐)\n\nSequentialLR([\n  LinearLR(start_factor=0.01, total_iters=warmup_epochs=5),\n  CosineAnnealingWarmRestarts(T_0=50, T_mult=2)\n], milestones=[warmup_epochs])\n\n周期: 50 → 100 → 200 epochs (T_mult=2 翻倍)\n备选: StepLR(step_size=80, gamma=0.5)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
