    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "val_text",
      "x": 760,
      "y": 678,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 175,
      "text": "Validation & Early Stopping\n\n验证: epoch % 20 == 0 → eval loop\n指标: trans/fwd/lat/ht + rot/roll/pitch/yaw\n\nEarly Stopping:\n  patience (默认 0=禁用)\n  counter++ when val 不改善\n  DDP: broadcast(stop, src=0) 同步\n\nCheckpoint: ckpt_{epoch}.pth (每40ep)\n           ckpt_best_val.pth (最优)",
      "originalText": "Validation & Early Stopping\n\n验证: epoch % 20 == 0 → eval loop\n指标: trans/fwd/lat/ht + rot/roll/pitch/yaw\n\nEarly Stopping:\n  patience (默认 0=禁用)\n  counter++ when val 不改善\n  DDP: broadcast(stop, src=0) 同步\n\nCheckpoint: ckpt_{epoch}.pth (每40ep)\n           ckpt_best_val.pth (最优)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
